Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat.\NHeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we here?\NWell, I'm glad we're here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because if we weren't here, we wouldn't\Nbe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:01:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I feel blessed by your presence\Nand I ask God to bless thee in the name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Lord. Amen.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I need this cane to beat off the women.\NThey're all after my little body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do\Nnow? What happens this morning,
