Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I think I have two of them here.\N>> Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> All right. What is it?\NThat's my friendly voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone wants to see see you know\Neverybody.
