Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody is being\Neverybody is doing the best they can at
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,any time. That's a good rule to\Nremember.
