Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.60,0:32:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just ask God to reveal to me the\Npurpose of the primary purpose of this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.96,0:32:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,time and this lifetime.\N>> Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.03,0:33:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Very good. Thank you.\N>> Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.39,0:33:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Hi.\N>> Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.88,0:33:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um uh my question is related to an\Nexperience I had. Um I was on a extended
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.20,0:33:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,meditation retreat and I had taken vows\Nand surrendered my life to God. And
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.15,0:33:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,during that retreat uh we\Nwere to learn a special technique and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.88,0:33:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,out of pride as well as uh just not\Nbeing open to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.32,0:33:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,um stop getting the technique. I\Nreceived the technique before
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.08,0:33:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> understanding him. You was on a retreat\Nwhich was devoted to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.84,0:33:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,>> To God.\N>> Speak slowly please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.91,0:33:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\N>> Devoted to of course I was it was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.20,0:33:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,essentially a meditation retreat.\N>> A meditation retreat. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.64,0:33:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And I to receive a special meditation\Ntechnique.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.00,0:34:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh.\N>> And I received it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.03,0:34:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that if you receive it too\Nearly that you can actually totally mess
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.32,0:34:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,up\Num your ability to be have a continuous
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,experience of the silence.\NSo
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.83,0:34:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,>> wait a minute\N>> I'll I'll try and paraphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.91,0:34:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Don't run on it.\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.48,0:34:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> What he's saying uh the teaching is\Nfalse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.52,0:34:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay. Thank you.\NSo I essentially I've been doing the 12
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.39,0:34:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,steps and there's just I've I'd released\Nthis
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.24,0:34:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,um and I've spoke about it. Um so\Nessentially that belief is incorrect is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.52,0:34:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're saying.\N>> Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.63,0:34:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> That's what the arm says. Don't quote\Nme.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.20,0:34:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay.\N>> Okay. Um because the essentially my
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.28,0:34:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,question is the belief is around the\Nfact that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.83,0:35:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,um in that experience I had forsaken my\Nrelationship with God in this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.44,0:35:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um\N>> where did you get that message from?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.83,0:35:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,>> From from what happened during the\Nexperience. It was more an internal
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.32,0:35:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thing not so much from others. But\Nessentially since that point I've been
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.76,0:35:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,meditating a lot, doing spiritual work\Nand my experience continues to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.24,0:35:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a belief that\Nor I believe I have a block
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.83,0:35:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to experiencing the silence continually\Nall the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.64,0:35:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which is what I'd like to is to\Nexperience the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.11,0:35:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times. And I have I feel that I\Nhave a block to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.00,0:35:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I just wondered if you have any\Nadvice for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.64,0:35:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> You want to experience the presence of\NGod at all times, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.72,0:35:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.00,0:36:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you just do that?\N>> That is a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.24,0:36:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay no attention to the passing street\Ncars and the passing women
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.56,0:36:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and people dangling money in front of\Nyour nose for one thing or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.44,0:36:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind that God it prevails at all\Ntimes and in all places and in all
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.48,0:36:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,situations.\NThe presence of God is continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.92,0:36:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the weather. You can stop now\Nand notice the sunshine is sh sh sh sh
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.56,0:36:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh\Nsh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.64,0:36:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh sh shining or\Nnot not notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.92,0:36:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But whether you notice it or not doesn't\Naffect the fact that the sun is shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.96,0:36:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand? It's just a matter of\Nwhat you want to focus on, what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.04,0:36:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to look at.\NI can look at the quietude in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:37:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or I can look at the sun coming in the\Nwindows. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.11,0:37:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's not God coming up and then\Ndisappearing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.96,0:37:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just noticing what you notice.\NSo you accept life as you experience it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.32,0:37:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolding.\NRight at this moment you are here
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.16,0:37:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to me and within a few seconds\Nyou'll be out in the room going that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.80,0:37:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,way. And uh that's the way it's supposed\Nto be. continuous change and movement
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.59,0:37:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,etc.\NAnd uh you tell yourself that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.32,0:37:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's desirable. If God wanted\Nit to be different, it would be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.28,0:37:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If God wanted it to be different, it\Nwould be
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.44,0:37:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,simple enough.\N>> Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.88,0:38:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Could I shake your hand and get a\Npicture?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.80,0:38:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N>> Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.68,0:38:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If God wanted things to be different,\Nthey would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.56,0:38:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here to become enlightened.\NWe're enlightened, we wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.35,0:38:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we don't have to feel ashamed that\Nwe're not enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.32,0:38:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We come here to become so to move us\Nalong the pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.48,0:38:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Hi. Yes.\N>> Will you own for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.32,0:38:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> What?\N>> That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.64,0:38:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> You want a big M or a little M?\N>> Big one. Let's do a big
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.07,0:38:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh, a big M. Oh, golly Wizard.\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.72,0:39:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good.\N>> May I also shake your hand and yours
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.00,0:39:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,too?\N>> What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.00,0:39:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> She wants to touch your hand.\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.88,0:39:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> The last time I was up here, I was a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.32,0:39:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,little too nervous to look into the\Ndoc's eyes. I was wondering if I could
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.16,0:40:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,look into his eyes.\NI can't hear what he's saying. What is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.44,0:40:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he saying?\N>> Just look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.48,0:40:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Right. Thank you very much.\N>> The eyes have the window to the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.20,0:40:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh.\NDr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.16,0:40:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> I came here to offer my prostrations and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.76,0:40:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,receive your blessings. Please allow me\Nto do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.56,0:40:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> He wants to\N>> He's a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.04,0:40:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.40,0:40:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I don't know.\N>> From India.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.24,0:40:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> From India.\N>> Oh. Oh. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.76,0:40:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Better call when they're from India.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.11,0:41:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.76,0:41:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harder to be a monk in the world\Nthan out of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.96,0:41:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N>> First, I would like to thank you for all
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.64,0:41:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,your teachings.\NI have a question about uh the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.59,0:41:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,connection between selfless service and\Nuh the inner work
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.40,0:41:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> they're both the same.\NSo then the question is when I see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.28,0:41:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,something happens in the world and I\Nthere's a response coming from inside my
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.68,0:41:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,mind do I have to recontextualize\Nand or recontextualize and do something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.92,0:42:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,about it\N>> when he sees something happening in the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.11,0:42:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,world does he have to recontextualize it\Nor and induce act on it or Oh, it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.24,0:42:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on where he is in the evolution\Nof his spirit. Uh, I think it's God's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.80,0:42:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,problem. See, you may figure you got to\Nhelp the street car get back on the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.56,0:42:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,track. And I figure it's God's problem.\N>> So, where is the selfless service? Uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.76,0:42:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,where does the service come into\Npicture? If I
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.88,0:42:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> contextually contextualize it as a God's\Nproblem,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.04,0:42:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,>> where do I act?\N>> When you give Yeah. selfless service and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.68,0:42:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,inner work and you said it's one and the\Nsame. So when does he
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.28,0:42:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,>> do the selfless service\N>> uh
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.80,0:42:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and um\N>> be of service to the world at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.88,0:43:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any separation of the two.\N>> If I don't see a problem where where do
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.68,0:43:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I serve?\N>> If Yeah. So he's looking for a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.44,0:43:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to solve so he can't search. So\N>> no that's that's defective
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.76,0:43:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that's\N>> looking for problems is not the way to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.76,0:43:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,find out anything about anything.\N>> So Southwest service should be done with
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.76,0:43:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,without a heavy heart. It should be done\Nwith an open heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.88,0:43:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes. Mhm.\NAnd uh it's artificial to like look for
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.92,0:43:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a problem.\NI mean what do you think is a problem is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.07,0:43:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in your head?\NThere aren't any problems in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.28,0:43:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So we just sit and meditate or\N>> what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.44,0:43:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, you know, in ashrams there's\Nalways things that need to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.68,0:43:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\N>> You know, so that's selfless service.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.16,0:43:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But\N>> oh
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.83,0:44:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> but so that's what he's saying is he\Nsays do you just sit and meditate and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.00,0:44:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,just ask or is there when do you uh\Nrespond?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.20,0:44:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So he has a conflict between\Nuh striving for enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.28,0:44:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> right\N>> and service to the world. That's an
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.07,0:44:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,artificial dichotomy. There is no\Ndifference between the two. You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.59,0:44:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be sweeping the street and uh or\Nsitting cross-legged and meditating.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.68,0:44:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both the same.\NSweeping the street is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.64,0:44:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, in other words, he can be service\Nwhether he's sweeping the street or
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.44,0:44:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,whether he's meditating, he's still\Nservice to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.40,0:44:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, he's defining service in what he\Ncalls service,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.96,0:44:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> right?\N>> So then he it's just the definition he
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.24,0:44:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,makes up. If he thinks this is a service\Nto the world, then that's service to the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.76,0:45:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,world.\NBut if I say it's irrelevant to the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.00,0:45:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,world, then it's not service anymore.\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.24,0:45:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So service to the world is whatever you\Ndefine as service to the world. Keeping
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.59,0:45:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the way and staying silent is the\Nbest way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.00,0:45:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> One more question. Uh I when I witness\Nthe thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.72,0:45:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> what\N>> when he witnesses the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.76,0:45:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> How do I take the next step from
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.72,0:45:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessing to the next deeper\Nstate?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.40,0:45:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> What is the next deeper state?\N>> You're in a deeper state. Witnessing is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.24,0:45:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what's happening all the time.\NThe mind is doing witnessing all the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.44,0:45:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,time. It doesn't need you to tell it to\Ngo ahead and witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.04,0:46:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights go on. You notice that the\Nlights go on. You didn't say to your
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.56,0:46:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,mind, "Mind, please watch and notice\Nwhether the lights go on." It's
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.52,0:46:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,happening spontaneously. So you don't\Nhave to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.68,0:46:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,um\Ndo anything about it because that's what
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.00,0:46:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind is is doing automatically\Nbecause of its quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.68,0:46:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So just let the mind do what it does. It\Njust notices
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.76,0:46:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,things spontaneously\Nand autonomously.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.31,0:46:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So we allow the mind to just be\Nautonomously that which it is already
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.80,0:46:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it doesn't need your help to be told\Nwhat to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.96,0:46:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell your mind notice\Neverything going on around here. That's
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.48,0:46:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,what it's doing.\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.20,0:46:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And and that's the step. Is there\Nanything else needs to be done or it's
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.40,0:46:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,>> No, you keep pushing for something to\Ndo. Let go of D do D do D do D do D do D
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.16,0:47:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,do D do D do D do D do D O\Nsay just B
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.88,0:47:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,okay\N>> I would seek uh blessings from you on my
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.04,0:47:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual journey.\N>> God bless you on your spiritual journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.48,0:47:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.\NCall the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.48,0:47:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.48,0:47:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Uh-huh.\NI'm going to have something in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.20,0:47:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your arm.\NResist. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.80,0:47:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Hi,\N>> Dr. Hawkins. Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.35,0:47:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I'm from India.\N>> I'm from India.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.72,0:47:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> She's from India.\N>> Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.88,0:48:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I've been in this country for last about\N30 years. And yesterday was a very
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.64,0:48:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,significant day in our lives which is\Ncalled Guru Purima that's called in
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.52,0:48:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,India.\N>> Terrible time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.72,0:48:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Guru is master Purima is yesterday was a\Nfull
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.96,0:48:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,>> full moon day where we have tribute to\NGuru Parara. I I'm just here to seek
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.68,0:48:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,your blessings since this was only\Nyesterday. And I love you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.24,0:48:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> God bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.28,0:48:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless India.\NHow many times have we lived in India
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.24,0:48:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,already? I hate to think of it.\NRotate through India.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.92,0:48:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,India is like spiritual headquarters.\N>> We've all probably lived 20 30 lives in
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.76,0:48:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,India.\N>> Yeah.
