Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.71,1:50:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Grateful for thee oh Lord. Grateful for\Nthe love of my brother and my sister
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.48,1:50:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and for all of life.\NSo we give thanks to thee, oh Lord, for
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.52,1:51:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,our life.\N>> Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.71,1:51:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,>> That's it.\NI squeezed them all at once, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.63,1:51:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I squeezed everybody all at once.\NBoy, I'm pooped.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.67,1:51:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.36,1:52:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.80,1:52:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're blessed by the presence of each\Nother.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.00,1:52:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Each one of us here\N>> is thereby blessing everybody else here
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.48,1:52:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,>> because we dedicate ourselves to God.\NWe have a capacity that does not occur
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.80,1:52:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise.\N>> So we are grateful for that gift from
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.96,1:53:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the old Lord.\NWe are grateful for thy love and thy
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.48,1:53:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,presence\Nand thy gift of being able to bless
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.40,1:53:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,others through thy love and divine\Npresence.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.04,1:53:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Amen.\N>> Let's all say amen together.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.63,1:53:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Amen. That's it.\NOkay folks, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.15,1:54:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful for your presence today.\NEverything's divine,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.19,1:54:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> especially Susie.\NI'm so
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.76,1:54:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,grateful for the gift of her love,\N>> for the love of all beings, but
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.23,1:54:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,especially for her\Ncuz uh she came into my life to be with
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.80,1:54:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,me.\N>> She was the only one willing to put up
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.11,1:54:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with me.\NThey asked for volunteers in Evan and
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.76,1:54:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,she raised her hand\Nthereby undoing all her past negative
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.71,1:54:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,karma.\NBut when do we go this time? Where do I
